narrative.whyNow: Fixing Sequence (hips late / low separation) gives you the biggest one move gain right now-better starts, better strike, less chaos.
narrative.avoidList: Avoid chasing more speed today. Clean contact and sequence first.
narrative.confidenceCue: Expect a small confidence dip while you change the pattern. That's normal-stay calm, take slower reps, and measure progress by contact + start line.
